==Latin==

===Etymology===
From Latin ''[[trans|tr&#257;ns]]'' + ''[[ferre]]''.

===Verb===
('''tr&#257;nsfer&#333;''', '''tr&#257;nsferre''', '''tr&#257;nstul&#299;''', '''tr&#257;nsl&#257;tum''')
# to bear across; to [[transfer]]

